starterPokemon.gible=It skulks in caves, and when prey or an enemy passes by, it leaps out and chomps them. It often gets itself hurt in the process.
starterPokemon.dratini=It is called the "Mirage PokГ©mon" because so few have seen it. Its shed skin has been found.
starterPokemon.charcadet=Burnt charcoal came to life and became a PokГ©mon. Possessing a fiery fighting spirit, Charcadet will battle even tough opponents.
starterPokemon.litwick=The glow of Litwick's flame is powered by the life energy that it absorbs from people and PokГ©mon.
starterPokemon.mareanie=Mareanie have vicious dispositions, so they are often cast out by other PokГ©mon living in the sea and made to fend for themselves.
starterPokemon.lillipup=The long hair around its face provides an amazing radar that lets Lillipup sense subtle changes in its surroundings.
starterPokemon.buneary=When it senses danger, it perks up its ears. On cold nights, it sleeps with its head tucked into its fur.
starterPokemon.beldum=It uses magnetic waves to converse with its kind, all joined by a single brain.
starterPokemon.ralts=It is highly attuned to the emotions of people and PokГ©mon. It hides if it senses hostility.
starterPokemon.eevee=Its ability to evolve into many forms allows it to adapt smoothly and perfectly to any environment.
starterPokemon.pikachu=When several of these PokГ©mon gather, their electricity could build and cause lightning storms.
starterPokemon.munchlax=It wolfs down its weight in food once a day, swallowing food whole with almost no chewing.
starterPokemon.fletchling=These friendly PokГ©mon send signals to one another with beautiful chirps and tail-feather movements.
starterPokemon.larvitar=Born deep underground, this PokГ©mon becomes a pupa after eating enough dirt to make a mountain.
starterPokemon.larvesta=When attacked, Larvesta spits fire from its five horns to repel its enemies.
starterPokemon.aron=It eats iron ore to make its body grow. When it evolves, its entire body becomes like steel.
starterPokemon.swablu=It constantly grooms its cotton-like wings. It takes a shower to clean itself if it becomes dirty.
starterPokemon.bagon=Its well-developed jaw is powerful enough to crush stone. It dreams of one day soaring through the sky.
starterPokemon.riolu=It can read the emotions of people and PokГ©mon. It will only open up to a Trainer who is a worthy partner.
starterPokemon.rotom=One boy's invention led to a new PokГ©mon being born. It has an affinity for all things electrical.
starterPokemon.hatenna=It senses the feelings of other living things. It prefers quiet places, away from crowds.
starterPokemon.dreepy=If this weak PokГ©mon is by itself, a mere child could defeat it. However, if Dreepy has friends to help it train, it can evolve and become much stronger.
starterPokemon.tinkatink=This PokГ©mon pounds iron bits together in order to make a hammer. It will appear at human dwellings and steal tools for materials.
starterPokemon.rookidee=It will bravely challenge any opponent, no matter how powerful. This PokГ©mon gets pumped up when its wings are ruffled by strong winds.
starterPokemon.axew=They play with each other by knocking their large tusks together. Their tusks break sometimes, but they grow back.
starterPokemon.mawile=It chomps with its gaping mouth. Its huge jaws are actually steel horns that have been transformed.
starterPokemon.scyther=It slashes through grass with its sharp scythes, moving too fast for the human eye to track.
starterPokemon.toxel=It manipulates the chemical makeup of its poison to produce electricity. The voltage is weak, but it can cause a tingling paralysis.
starterPokemon.lotad=It searches about for clean water. If it does not drink water for too long, the leaf on its head wilts.
starterPokemon.shroomish=It spouts poison spores to repel foes. It prefers damp, dark places.
